
NANO PIN → CONNECTS TO
─────────────────────────────────
D8  → NRF24L01 CSN (pin 4)
D7  → NRF24L01 CE (pin 3)
D9  → SERVO SIGNAL (Orange wire)
D10 → RESERVED / FUTURE SERVO 2
D11 → NRF24L01 MOSI (pin 6)
D12 → NRF24L01 MISO (pin 7)
D13 → NRF24L01 SCK (pin 5)

A4 (SDA) → MPU6050 SDA + BMP280 SDA
A5 (SCL) → MPU6050 SCL + BMP280 SCL

5V       → MPU6050 VCC + BMP280 VCC
3.3V     → NRF24L01 VCC (pin 2)

GND      → ALL: NRF GND (pin 1) + MPU GND + BMP GND + Servo Brown

POWER:
Power Bank 5V → NANO Vin/VCC (for logic)
18650 → MT3608 Boost → 5V → Servo Red wire
Servo Brown → Common GND

NRF24L01 Module Pinout:
NRF24L01 PIN → NANO PIN
───────────────────────
1 GND       → GND
2 VCC       → 3.3V
3 CE        → D7
4 CSN       → D8
5 SCK       → D13
6 MOSI      → D11
7 MISO      → D12
8 IRQ       → NOT CONNECTED

Servo Connection:
SERVO WIRE → NANO PIN
─────────────────────
Orange (Signal) → D9
Red (Power)     → 5V from 18650 (NOT from NANO!)
Brown (Ground)  → GND

I2C Sensors (MPU6050 & BMP280):
SHARED I2C BUS:
MPU6050 SDA → A4
MPU6050 SCL → A5
BMP280 SDA  → A4 (same wire)
BMP280 SCL  → A5 (same wire)
MPU6050 VCC → 5V
BMP280 VCC  → 5V
BOTH GND    → GND

